column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,  s.specobjid, s.z as Redshift,  # * s.z/# as Distance,  (.#*(p.g - p.r) +.#) as Color,  (p.g+.#*(p.g-p.r) +.#) as Magnitude FROM   PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class = &&&  AND (# * (s.z/#))<# AND Distance >#  AND (.#*(p.g - p.r) +.#) <#
